markets.guidance:
Winner(incl. overtime)

Predict which team will be the winner.*include overtime

  •  Home bet wins if the Home team wins the match.
  •  Away bet wins if the Away team wins the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time(include overtime) including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Winner (incl. OT)

markets.guidance:
O/U(incl. overtime)

Predict if the total score during the entire match is over/under a given line/spread indicated.*include overtime

This market has 2 possible outcomes at regular time i.e. Over x.5 or Under x.5. For example (Ov/Un 150.5)

  •  Over 150.5 bet wins if there are 151 or more points scored.(e.g. the result of match is 90:80, 100:95, 80:72, etc.)
  •  Under 150.5 bet wins if there are 150 or fewer points scored.(e.g. the result of match is 80:70, 75:70, 60:70, etc)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time(include overtime) including all injury and stoppage time.

markets.guidance:
1x2

This market has 3 possible outcomes at *Regular Time.

The following options are available:

  •  Home WIN (1) bet wins if Home team wins the match. (e.g. the result of the match is 100:99, 100:98, 80:78, etc.)
  •  Draw (X) bet wins if the teams draw at regular time. (e.g. the result of the match is 100:100, 88:88, 68:68, etc.)
  •  Away WIN (2) bet wins if Away team wins the match. (e.g. the result of the match is 80:98, 90:100, 88:90, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: 1x2
markets.title: 1,X,2

markets.guidance:
HT/FT Result

Predict the result of a match both at the 1st half time and full time.*Regualr time

The following options are available:

  •  1/1 bet wins if Home team leads after the 1st half and also wins the match.
  •  1/X bet wins if Home team leads after the 1st half and match ends in draw.
  •  1/2 bet wins if Home team leads after the 1st half and the Away team wins the match.
  •  X/1 bet wins if the 1st half ends in draw and the Home team wins the match.
  •  X/X bet wins if the 1st half ends in draw and also the match ends in draw.
  •  X/2 bet wins if the 1st half ends in draw and Away team wins the match.
  •  2/1 bet wins if Away team leads after the 1st half and Home team wins the match.
  •  2/X bet wins if Away team leads after the 1st half and match ends in draw.
  •  2/2 bet wins if Away team leads after the 1st half and also wins the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Halftime/fulltime

markets.guidance:
1st half - 1x2

This market has 3 possible outcomes at *First half.

The following options are available:

  •  Home bet wins if Home team scores ahead of Away team in the first half.
  •  Draw bet wins if Home team and Away team score the same in the first half.
  •  Away bet wins if Away team scores ahead of Home team in the first half.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its first half time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: 1st half - 1x2

markets.guidance: Which team will win after the 1st half?In the event of a draw bets in this market are void.
markets.name: 1st half - DNB

markets.guidance:
1st half - handicap

Predict what will the result be after the allotted handicap is applied to the point at the.*First half

The following options are available(For example the allotted handicap is 0.5):

  •  Home(+0.5) bet wins if Home team leads by any number of points in the first half, or the teams draw in the first half.
  •  Away(-0.5) bet wins if Away team leads by at least 1 point in the first half.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its first half time including all injury and stoppage time.

Predict what will the result be after the allotted handicap is applied to the point at the.*Second half

The following options are available(For example the allotted handicap is 0.5):

  •  Home(+0.5) bet wins if Home team leads by any number of points in the first half, or the teams draw in the second half.
  •  Away(-0.5) bet wins if Away team leads by at least 1 point in the second half.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its second half time including all injury and stoppage time.

  •  Yes bet wins if there is overtime in the match.
  •  No bet wins if there is no overtime in the match.

markets.guidance:
Home O/U(incl. overtime)

Predict if the Home team has more or less points than the given line.*include overtime

This market has 2 possible outcomes at regular time. i.e. Over x.5 or Under x.5. For example (Ov/Un 80.5)

  •  Over 80.5 bet wins if Home team scores 81 or more points at full time.(e.g. the result of match is 81:75, 100:90, 95:90, etc.)
  •  Under 80.5 bet wins if Home team scores 80 or less points at full time.(e.g. the result of match is 80:90, 75:82, 69:70, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time(include overtime) including all injury and stoppage time.

markets.guidance:
Odd/Even(incl. overtime)

Predict if the total number of points in the match is odd (151,153,155,...) or even (160,162,164,...). Own goals count.*include overtime

The following options are available:

  •  Odd bet wins if the match ends with an odd number of total points - 151,153,155,157...(e.g. the result of this match is 80:71, 83:90, 91:86, etc.)
  •  Even bet wins if the match ends with an even number of total points -160,162,164,166...（e.g. the result of this match is 80:80, 92:88, 82:70, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time(include overtime) including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Odd/Even (incl. overtime)

markets.guidance:
Highest scoring quarter

Predict the teams scoring highest in which quarter.*Regular time

The following options are available:

  •  1st quarter bet wins if the teams scoring highest in the 1st quarter.
  •  2nd quarter bet wins if the teams scoring highest in the 2nd quarter.
  •  3rd quarter bet wins if the teams scroing highest in the 3rd quarter.
  •  4th quarter bet wins if the teams scoring highest in the 4th quarter.
  •  Equal bet wins if the teams scoring equal in four quarters.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Highest scoring quarter

  •  Home WIN (1) bet wins if Home team takes the lead in the 2nd quarter.
  •  Draw (X) bet wins if the teams draw in the 2nd quarter.
  •  Away WIN (2) bet wins if Away team takes the lead in the 2nd quarter.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its specified quarter including all injury and stoppage time.

markets.guidance:
Winning margin(incl.overtime)

Predict by how many points the winning team wins the match.*Include overtime

The following options are available:

  •  Home by 14+ bet wins if Home wins Away 14 or more points.(e.g. the result of the match including overtime is 88:70, 100:86, etc.)
  •  Home by 7-13 bet wins if Home wins Away 7-13 points.(e.g. the result of the match including overtime is 90:77, 100:93, etc.)
  •  Home by 1-6 bet wins if Home wins Away 1-6 points.(e.g. the result of the match including overtime is 100:99, 88:82, etc.)
  •  Away by 1-6 bet wins if Away wins Home 1-6 points.(e.g. the result of the match including overtime is 85:90, 90:91, etc.)
  •  Away by 7-13 bet wins if Away wins Home 7-13 points.(e.g. the result of the match including overtime is 93:100, 90:103, etc.)
  •  Away by 14+ bet wins if Away wins Home 14 or more points.(e.g. the result of the match including overtime is 88:102, 85:100, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time(include overtime) including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Winning margin (incl. overtime)

markets.guidance:
Winner & O/U (incl. overtime)

Combo:Winner at full time including overtime & total points over/under the given line.

The following options are available(for example O/U 150.5):

  •  Home & Over 150.5 bet wins if Home wins the match and the number of total points at full time including overtime is 151 or more.(e.g. the result of the match is 100:80, 99:60, etc.)
  •  Away & Over 150.5 bet wins if Away wins the match and the number of total points at full time including overtime is 151 or more.(e.g. the result of the match is 80:100, 85:90, etc.)
  •  Home & Under 150.5 bet wins if Home wins the match and the number of total points at full time including overtime is less than 151.(e.g. the result of the match is 80:70, 78:71, etc.)
  •  Away & Under 150.5 bet wins if Away wins the match and the number of total points at full time including overtime is less than 151.(e.g. the result of the match is 70:80, 71:78, etc.)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time(include overtime) including all injury and stoppage time.
